        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1359283352" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6588051979423649699">This is a great collection of short stories from Shirley Jackson. Looking at some reviews, I think some people have heard Stephen King cite Jackson as one of his favourite authors and gone into this collection expecting it to be full of horror stories. This is isn’t the case. Jackson writes well in many different genres and this collection displays her versatility. I enjoyed this book a great deal. Individual story ratings listed below.<br/><br/>1. &apos;The Intoxicated&apos; - 4 stars<br/>2. &apos;The Demon Lover&apos; - 3.5 sta</span>
  <span id="freeText6588051979423649699" style="display:none">This is a great collection of short stories from Shirley Jackson. Looking at some reviews, I think some people have heard Stephen King cite Jackson as one of his favourite authors and gone into this collection expecting it to be full of horror stories. This is isn’t the case. Jackson writes well in many different genres and this collection displays her versatility. I enjoyed this book a great deal. Individual story ratings listed below.<br /><br />1. 'The Intoxicated' - 4 stars<br />2. 'The Demon Lover' - 3.5 stars<br />3. ‘Like Mother Used to Make' - 4 stars<br />4. ‘Trial By Combat’ – 4 stars<br />5. ‘The Villager’ - 4 stars<br />6. 'My Life With R.H. Macy' - 5 stars<br />7. 'The Witch' - 5 stars<br />8. 'The Renegade' - 3.5 stars<br />9. 'After You, My Dear Alphonse' - 3.5 stars<br />10. 'Charles' - 3.5 stars<br />11. 'Afternoon in Linen' - 3 stars<br />12. ‘Flower Garden’ - 5 stars<br />13. ‘Dorothy and My Grandmother and the Sailors’ - 4 stars<br />14. ‘Colloquy’ - 5 stars<br />15. ‘Elizabeth’ - 3.5 stars<br />16. ‘A Fine Old Firm’ - 3.5 stars<br />17. ‘The Dummy’ - 4 stars<br />18. ‘Seven Types of Ambiguity’ - 5 stars<br />19. ‘Come Dance With Me in Ireland’ - 3.5 stars<br />20. ‘Of Course’ - 4.5 stars<br />21. ‘Pillar of Salt’ - 4.5 stars<br />22. ‘Men With Their Big Shoes’ - 4 stars<br />23. ‘The Tooth’ - 4 stars<br />24. ‘Got a Letter from Jimmy’ - 3.5 stars<br />25. ‘The Lottery’ - 5 stars<br /><br />Overall - 4 stars<br /><br />My next book: <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3300357556" rel="nofollow noopener">Marvel Masterworks: Deathlok vol. 1</a></span>
